			<pluginExecution> <pluginExecutionFilter> <groupId>org.jacoco</groupId> <artifactId>jacoco-maven-plugin</artifactId> 
			<version>0.7.0.201403182114</version> <goals> <goal>prepare-agent</goal> 
			</goals> </pluginExecutionFilter> <action> m2e doesn't know what to do with 
